  "instructions": [
    "Heat 2 tablespoons of olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the bresaola and cook until flaky, about 4-6 minutes.",
    "Add smoked paprika, garlic powder, black pepper, and salt. Cook for an additional minute.",
    "Stir in muhammara paste and crack wheat. Cook for 2 minutes, until heated through.",
    "Add shredded mozzarella and stir until melted and well combined.",
    "Stir in parsley and lemon juice. Cook for an additional minute, until heated through.",
    "Transfer to a serving platter and garnish with additional parsley, if desired."
